////////////////////////////////////
/     Steps to constroy the api    /
////////////////////////////////////

1) Command dotnet new webapi -n <name>
2)Create the CommandsController.cs 
3)Create the Models folder and the Command.cs
4)Install dotnet ef
5) Create de Dbcontext class CommandContext.cs 
6)Create the connection String on appsetting.json
7)Configure the context on Startup.cs, with dependence injection of IConfiguration interface
8)Add migration with command dotnet ef migrations add <name>
9)Update database with command dotnet ef database update 
10)start creating the end points on the controller
